Title: Collateral Damage
Plot: A Navy bank has been robbed. NCIS is responsible for the investigation. One of the new recruits assigned to the fraud unit, Special Agent Dwayne Wilson, joins the team to help.
ParentalRatingReason: R13 Violence and horror scenes. Content may disturb
